{"tid":1719022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基督徒接放學 (亦不得不佩服警方戰術運用)","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T13:34:32.000Z","uid":194955,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed4d647cb6ebf3c870e4a74cff24193995c5ea5","tid":1719022,"uid":194955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"利申：小信徒，唔希望再見到有人死。<br />\n一直冇參與運動，但因為有重要嘅人被困大學宿舍，所以出POST。<br />\n<br />\n見到大家未明警方點解會攻擊大學。試下俾大家一個觀點：示威者覺得警察宿舍係班警察春袋嘅同時，大學學生宿舍/大學校園同時成為班大學生嘅春袋。<br />\n<br />\n情況可以理解成雙方攻城戰。但由於警方固有武力優勢，示威者會處於守勢。<br />\n所謂久守必失，警方唔攻入中大，并唔係因為攻唔入，只係將部分中大學生困守學園，係留個誘餌係到(Decoy)，再利用固有組織優勢同交通機動力優勢，反覆進攻不同大學，令示威者兩邊走。<br />\n記住，沒有永遠攻不下的城，想攻入中大，視乎前線想向學生開幾多槍實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長遠死守後果係點，唔需多講，請自行想像。<br />\n<br />\n破局關鍵係 ---------- <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">空城!</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">住Hall嘅請撤Hall返屋企，返唔到嘅搵朋友一齊，咪成為其他人嘅負累!</span></span><br />\n你可能會反駁：學園係我地屋企，點解要我地走，唔係警方離開?<br />\n但我會話：非常時期，唔好意氣用事，大學係死嘅(HKIX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，但人係生嘅，唔好因為要其他人守護你地而造成傷亡。應該戰略性撤退時，就走啦，留守只會亂左大局。真正嘅屋企唔係大學，而係香港。請為大局著想，唔好成為運動嘅負累。<br />\n<br />\n你可能都會問：Hall咁多人，呢個時勢點帶佢地走?<br />\n我會發夢：可以靠和理非同基督徒，以大規模接朋友放學方式(人道救援)，接佢地返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接得幾多個得幾多個，儘量減少留校人數。<br />\n<br />\n擅攻者，敵不知其所攻。擅守者，敵不知其所守。<br />\n願神保守大家。"},{"pid":"3f18c7e9b00f9a3a4d9270cc6b41bf794ba52f91","tid":1719022,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c315a415550363801c59809e540b1fcb11c74ef","tid":1719022,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"0c272ac293bd830a02b972d0df1a25f9ef66f0cd","tid":1719022,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e0647df0a1eb112b32c3fd9d581c5d00baeb1077","tid":1719022,"uid":194955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bb0b7f4ed50100ba9633ee8b08c9da98525fd9","tid":1719022,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe5816b2278e13c43e140b33c8f2ad536f0022c2","tid":1719022,"uid":114347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"4e1e693f9ffb4cb3c1df236ca4e26a1311d95111","tid":1719022,"uid":263926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"Push ah<br />\n養完兵 研究完好快啲出番嚟"},{"pid":"73f2daa9987db6ec7908885d5e9aecad2b9ec066","tid":1719022,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線 ：向外國報告校園情況！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719066</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retwe